{"tid":2293510,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府放生中資化驗所 不公佈4的士司機樣本受污染假陽性醜聞","createTime":"2020-11-20T09:42:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T02:44:26.000Z","uid":56115,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"fc9f78f4490f958fbf3e6c082be6e9f4f7812eef","tid":2293510,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T09:42:14.000Z","msg":"承接政府多個檢測項目的<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">金域檢驗（香港）</span></span>有限公司，出現懷疑假陽性個案。早前同日確診的4名的士司機，入院後全部檢測樣本呈陰性，體內亦無抗體，有專家懷疑是化驗所將4人樣本污染才出現假陽性結果。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，上述4宗懷疑假陽性個案，均是11月11日初步確診、11月12日確診的士司機，年齡47歲至77歲。他們連同當日確診的一名復康巴士司機，<span class=\"red\">均是接受由金域負責的特定群組檢測後轉介衞生署</span>。<br />\n<br />\n檢測出現假陽性，或有機會令無辜人士反而在院內受感染。早前一名尼泊爾男子便被誤當確診者送院，翌日才發現出錯，該男子出院兩周後死亡，死因有待死因庭確定。"},{"pid":"c004ca51feeda3dcb98bbbd9cb6dffc2bda42a46","tid":2293510,"uid":56115,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T09:42:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201120/42BXNGN7HJCIDJMRBVE5VYYJOU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201120%2F42BXNGN7HJCIDJMRBVE5VYYJOU%2F&d=gxBKi3yaaNwv0eARaXv6BfFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=c1913454\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201120%2F42BXNGN7HJCIDJMRBVE5VYYJOU%2F&h=9779225b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201120/42BXNGN7HJCIDJMRBVE5VYYJOU/</a>"},{"pid":"8b93ff76882edc02f941cac110b698c5a1fd45ea","tid":2293510,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T09:46:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5162577ac1e88a9fefa3c86d4364ffe1719a7517","tid":2293510,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T09:52:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b881ca19415a21501ca76713c79d482b4250d53a","tid":2293510,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":